# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CricAPI  →  https://cricapi.com  (free tier: 100 calls/day)
# 1. Sign up, copy your API key from the dashboard
# 2. Find the IPL 2025 series ID:
#    curl "https://api.cricapi.com/v1/series?apikey=YOUR_KEY&search=IPL"
#    Look for "Indian Premier League 2025" → copy its "id" field
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CRICKET_API_KEY=your_cricapi_key_here
IPL_SERIES_ID=your_ipl_2025_series_id_here
